OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain. Conditions will be
OL,8,Frather murky for Dumfries and
OL,9,FGalloway, with occasional mist and fog
OL,10,Fpatches.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with patchy
OL,13,Frain, clearing through the morning.
OL,14,FTurning brighter during the afternoon
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells developing and a few
OL,16,Fscattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
